result.name: election-results
result.notes:
Elections results data including name, party, number of votes, elected papers issued and papers rejected.

Also see:

*   [Election of Local Councillors - summary by party](https://www.calderdale.gov.uk/council/democracy/electionresults/summary.jsp?election=537)
*   [Council elections dashboard](https://opendata.calderdale.gov.uk/extensions/Elections/Elections.html)
*   [European Parliamentary Election](https://www.calderdale.gov.uk/council/democracy/electionresults/results.jsp?election=477)
